lead_paragraph: Max Pacioretty's second goal of the night lifted the Montreal Canadiens to a 4-3 victory over the Detroit Red Wings on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Pacioretty, Canadiens Play Spoiler With Win Over Red Wings
